snippet.title: Grandma Green Announcement Trailer
snippet.description: Play as an adorable grandma, bring talking plants to life, and cultivate the garden of your dreams in Grandma Green! "Help Grandma navigate the challenges of growing older and discover a new sense of belonging as she embarks on this new journey alone!" https://www.grandmagreen.app/ #indiegames #cozygames #farminggames
